      *OET do file
*By Phil Tian
*version 11.2

clear all

set mem 250m
set matsize 800
set more off

cd H:/

capture log close
log using "OET_log", replace
use oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta, clear

gen double ps=psexpectation/1000

program define OET_ML

args lnf sigma gamma
tempvar j
gen double `j'=ps-winpc^`gamma'/(winpc^`gamma'+(1-winpc)^`gamma')
quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(($ML_y1-`j')/`sigma'))-ln(`sigma')

end
